- Use the ButtonGroup to toggle between related options
- Use the boilerplate below when using the ButtonGroup component

### Default: Boilerplate

```jsx
<ButtonGroup
      groupAriaLabel="button group aria label"
      value={1}
      options={[
        {
          value: 1,
          text: "Alpha"
        },
        {
          value: 2,
          text: "Beta"
        },
        {
          value: 3,
          text: "Gamma"
        },
        {
          value: 4,
          text: "Delta"
        }
      ]}
    />
```

